    I

    ISymptomReader - Interface in com.hemebiotech.analytics
    Reads symptom data from a source and returns a list of strings, possibly with duplicates and unordered, or an empty list if no data is available.
    ISymptomWriter - Interface in com.hemebiotech.analytics
    Writes symptom data to a file, with each symptom on a new line, accepts a list of strings representing the symptoms, and has a method to retrieve symptom data from the file, returning a list of strings.
